	<h1 class="title">改造美国总统的“空军一号”是一种什么样的体验？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Michael Beschloss</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-08-13 07:33:41 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/13394/medium/13394.jpg?1439346523" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="13394" data-title="《改造美国总统的“空军一号”是一种什么样的体验？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/13394/medium/13394.jpg?1439346523" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/13394.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
